    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Wyvaran&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Flight&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Generations of wyvaran elders pass down tales that predate written history. While many ignore these or dismiss them as simple stories, others revere the lore of their elders. These wyvarans consider it their sacred duty to study the lost histories and pass them down to others. They gain a +2 racial bonus on two Knowledge skills of their choice. Those Knowledge skills are class skills for them. This racial trait replaces flight.  </p>",
